dcterms:description: The MEDIQA-M3G dataset consists of 842 train, 56 validation, and 100 test cases, each containing images of skin conditions and accompanying query text. The dataset is designed for generating clinical responses in dermatology, with responses provided in multiple languages including Chinese, English, and Spanish.
dcterms:title: MEDIQA-M3G Dataset
